                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 515.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner, Mary Ann Brown's, former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 1st Jan., 1844, and confined six months</hi>)—she is the person.</p>
